title: Team Leviathan is looking for a High Plat/Diamond ADC!
body: Team Leviathan is looking for a plat 2-diamond ADC! Team is going to be starting diamond leagues in the beginning of January! We are backed by the Y2E Org and have a coach and a manager for the team! If you are interested add me in game @Mr Otter or on discord: MoistPotato#2451! We are looking for open minded individuals who are not toxic and are willing to learn and grow with the team!
